{"title":"拔掉活动了的牙（西藏萨迦格言）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔掉活动了的牙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（西藏萨迦格言）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和坏人的关系，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕很久了也要割断；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活动了的牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔掉它才会使自己舒坦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有害的事那怕很小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要迅速地扑灭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的一线决口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往往酿成巨大水灾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专门搞分裂的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连好朋友也要离开他；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涧水不断地冲涮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连岩石都要裂出缝来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（王尧选译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}